Package com.prc.alp.liaison

Defines the constants used throughout the ALP/Cougaar external agent liaison capability.

See:
          Description

Interface Summary
LConstants.ALP A convenience interface for organizing all of the configurable constants associated with the ALP/Cougaar external agent liaisons, including those related to liaison administration, LiaisonManager, and LiaisonDeputy functions.
LConstants.CoABS A convenience interface for organizing all of the configurable constants associated with the ALP/Cougaar external agent liaisons related to the CoABS Grid, including CoABSLiaisonDeputy functions.
 

Class Summary
LConstants A convenience class for organizing all of the configurable constants associated with the ALP/Cougaar external agent liaison capability.
 

Package com.prc.alp.liaison Description

Defines the constants used throughout the ALP/Cougaar external agent liaison capability.
